  "original_title": "\u0dc4\u0dd0\u0da7\u0db1\u0dca \u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0db4\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dc0\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dad\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dc0 \u0dc0\u0dc4\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Hatton gas stations temporarily closed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The management of Cipetco and IOC filling stations in Hatton today (26) temporarily closed their filling stations due to lack of diesel and petrol in their reserves.",
        "The Hatton SLTB Depot Manager had earlier issued diesel fuel to private buses but the supply of diesel fuel to private buses was temporarily suspended from yesterday (25) due to non-availability of diesel fuel for private buses, said the Hatton SLTB Depot Manager.",
        "Due to the lack of diesel fuel, a number of private buses plying daily and short distances daily from the Hatton private bus stand have been taken out of service for 26 days and parked again. Drivers say they have not been able to get the fuel they need."
      ],
